      "writtenOn": "2019-01-23T22:54:32Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "So I reworked this as per the suggestion, and the difference is:\n* Removed the type switch, and hence the \"kind\" column, since it seems redundant.\n* json.RawMessage doesn\u0027t allow for indents, so the marshall\u0027ed json is no longer indented.\n\nThe previous output was not indented, so it\u0027s not a regression.  I have a slight preference of making JSON indented, but that means we have to use a heavier weight JSON renderer.  Or we can also use a javascript based JSON renderer.  What are your thoughts?",
      "parentUuid": "e9a5dfbe_0fa3102b",
      "revId": "626ebc3c16c0b9a1d36186e3760937a7ccac8f19",
